title: Mr Boukadoum receives the new ambassador of Colombia in Algeria
text: Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr Sabri Boukadoum, received Wednesday, Mr Jos√© Antonio Solarte Gomez, who gave him copies of credentials accrediting him as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of the Republic of Colombia in Algeria.

The meeting was an opportunity to review the ways and means of consolidating economic relations between the two countries, in addition to exchanging points of view on the latest developments recorded in Latin America and North Africa.
